ts of The Week</b>\nğŸ‘¼ Trinity\nâ˜€ï¸ Lumen\nğŸ’¡ Lani\nğŸ”± Ares (Player Level 20 Unlock)\n\nğŸ¯Â <b>Season 10 Kit Balance Changes</b>\nWith the changes to Team Upgrades and generator production rates, a number of kits have been adjusted to balance gameplay.\n\nğŸ¤¿Â <b>Axolotl Amy</b>\nRemoved dependence on Eras to purchase additional axolotls.\nShield Axolotl Cost: 30 iron â†’ 50 iron\nDamage Axolotl Cost: 60 iron â†’ 100 iron\nBreak Speed Axolotl Cost: 80 iron â†’ 2 emeralds\nHealth Regen Axolotl Cost: 4 emeralds â†’ 6 emeralds\n\nğŸ£Â <b>Taliyah</b>\nTaliyah now upgrades her chickens through an item purchased in the shop..\nIron Armor Chicken Nest Cost: 120 iron\nDiamond Armor Chicken Nest Cost: 4 emeralds\nEmerald Armor Chicken Nest Cost: 6 emeralds\nVoid Armor Chicken Nest Cost: 10 emeralds\n\nğŸ§‘ğŸ¼â€ğŸŒ¾Â <b>Farmer Cletus</b>\nCarrot Seed Cost: 60 iron â†’ 70 iron\nCarrot Seed Growth Time: 2m 45s â†’ 3m 15s\nMelon Seed Growth Time: 2m 45s â†’ 3m 15s\n\nğŸª–Â <b>Drill</b>\nDrill Item Cost: 2 emeralds â†’ 3 emeralds\nMaximum number of drills on map per player: 3\n\nğŸÂ <b>Beekeeper Beatrix</b>\nBeehive Generator Cooldown: 8 seconds â†’ 10 seconds\n\nğŸª™Â <b>Metal Detector</b>\nIncreased time to scale to max rewards from finding Hidden Metal 15m â†’ 18\n\nâ›ï¸Â <b>Miner</b>\nReduced mining rewards by 15%\nReduced rewards from mid-game and late-game armor\n\n]]
